{"tid":2393613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一億公帑資助公務員子女赴英國留學","createTime":"2021-02-03T14:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T16:33:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"10ebf0590d685a5b865efaea0c3e74ca67589545","tid":2393613,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:28:14.000Z","msg":"約1600名公務員子女獲公帑資助留學英國　涉款1億元<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局回覆指，根據現行政策，只有在1996年8月1日之前按本地條款受聘的合資格公務員可為其留學英國的子女申領海外教育津貼，截至2020年12月31日，合資格領取海外教育津貼的公務員約5萬人。隨着符合資格申領海外教育津貼的公務員陸續退休，領取相關教育津貼的公務員人數亦會隨之減少。<br />\n<br />\n根據政府提交立法會的文件，2019至20財政年度有1,597名公務員申請子女海外教育津貼，1,347名學生獲資助就讀英國學校，涉及公帑約一億元。"},{"pid":"c413f36dbb9f3d1157c9eaf75ffcaf7d9f982b76","tid":2393613,"uid":41423,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:30:30.000Z","msg":"犯左國安法"},{"pid":"12863c83af414431898b6b2170ffc0c49a8a9ef5","tid":2393613,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"想問有冇得資助去支那留學？"},{"pid":"637e511522e82591768466e247b4bed2e07347eb","tid":2393613,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"英國終會將他們拋棄！"},{"pid":"453d38b29ea9164158f4e2dc24459d5246e1e56c","tid":2393613,"uid":357710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12863c83af414431898b6b2170ffc0c49a8a9ef5","tid":2393613,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"想問有冇得資助去支那留學？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"現在可以。"},{"pid":"03907266aa8e13994e873c88a3c41b727e1f9e70","tid":2393613,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:45:46.000Z","msg":"口𥚃說不"},{"pid":"1424b0983ef0b3d926969e40dff072190193f31c","tid":2393613,"uid":20438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"包括林痛"},{"pid":"66837dbc5340eb7e95442c789a4325ed64dfe12c","tid":2393613,"uid":299263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy